Ultimate Tokyo Travel Guide 🇯🇵✨

Planning a trip to Tokyo? Here’s your ultimate guide to the best spots in the city! Save this for your next adventure! 🗺️👇

📍 Must-Visit Places:

	•	Shibuya Crossing – Experience the world’s busiest intersection
	•	Shinjuku Golden Gai – Tiny bars, big vibes 🍶
	•	Senso-ji Temple – Tokyo’s oldest temple in Asakusa
	•	Harajuku & Takeshita Street – Kawaii culture & trendy shopping 🛍️
	•	Shibuya Sky – Epic city views 🌆
	•	Akihabara – Anime, gaming, and all things otaku 🎮
	•	Ginza – Luxury shopping & fine dining 💎
	•	TeamLab Planets – Mind-blowing digital art exhibition 🎨

Tag your travel buddy & start planning! ✈️🇯🇵 Save this for later!

Happy birthday to my best friend, my constant through all of life’s twists and turns. For over a decade, you’ve been my safe space, my biggest cheerleader, and the person who fills my life with endless joy. We’ve grown up together, witnessed each other’s highs and lows, and through it all, you’ve remained the most kind, strong, and beautiful soul. I am so incredibly proud of the woman you’ve become—someone with a heart of gold, who loves so deeply and gives so selflessly. I feel beyond blessed to have you by my side, and I can’t wait for all the beautiful moments ahead. Love you forever and always! ❤️✨

#bestiebirthday #happy30 #twinninginlife #friendslikefam #youngerandwiser #cheersto30🥂 #rideordie #milestonebirthday #france #friendswhotraveltogether

✨ Wrapping up my birthday month with so much gratitude! 🫶🏻
This past decade has been filled with growth, adventure, and unexpected joys, and I couldn’t be more thankful for the people who have made the journey so special. Celebrating with my closest friends and family reminded me how lucky I am to be surrounded by love, laughter, and endless support.

Here’s to new experiences, bigger dreams, and embracing every moment ahead! 🥂♥️
